                        <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOne">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>Submitty is one-of-a-kind, unique grading system where students and teachers can collaborate their tasks. With its simple yet elegant design, Submitty not only provides an ideal management system to its users but also helps them stay up-to-date with their dues. </p>
